headline: Jacobs Solutions Stock: How To Set Up A Long-Term Covered Call
summary: As we move into the softer seasonality, the desire to hop over the sticky bits is front and center. Today, we look at Jacobs Solutions (J) and study a leap covered call in Jacobs stock. A leap covered call refers to an option position that is well into the future, customarily one year or more. But our trade today is...
